docs.text: How to Add a New AM ¶ Change the date to reflect today's date on line 42 Select from else if to } copy it (ctl+c on Windows, cmd+c on Mac) Click next to } and press enter paste it (ctl+v on Windows, cmd+v on Mac) Select the name of the section you just copied and replace it with new name Find contact Id for their rep How to find T3's ID . Replace the Id listed with Id found in step 7 Press Save Button
docs.title: How to Add a New AM

docs.text: How to T3 Rep's Contact ID ¶ Open the Desk Contacts site at https://desk.zoho.com/support/luxerone/ShowHomePage.do#setup/users-control/agents/ Click next to New Agent button to search Type in the rep you are searching for Press enter Click on the name of the Rep The ID is the last part of the URL
